Morning, sir.

780
00:48:10,470 --> 00:48:12,888
Our days here in the jungle,
they start early.

781
00:48:13,098 --> 00:48:14,348
Morning, Daddy.

782
00:48:14,516 --> 00:48:17,143
That's my girl. See?
Already up and at 'em.

783
00:48:17,311 --> 00:48:18,352
Morning, sweetie.

784
00:48:19,354 --> 00:48:20,730
