786
00:48:23,442 --> 00:48:24,859
- Yeah, but...
- Hey, Dad.

787
00:48:25,027 --> 00:48:27,028
Aunt Mimi says
clay is good for your digestion.

788
00:48:27,195 --> 00:48:29,036
- Try some.
- No, sweetie. I just brushed my...

789
